snippet.title: Keira's world
snippet.description:
Hello people,
My name is Keira
I am 20 y/o
Arab origins and Muslim
Master student in process engineering
I opened this channel to share with you what I care about
I love the news so much I like to know what is going on in the world
I love fear movies
Clothes and makeup are my only concerns in this life as any other girl
I love to learn languages, I speak Arabic, French and English, and I have embarked on learning Spanish
My channel will be a cocktail
It means depending on the mood in which I wake up
If you want to be my friend on Facebook, just send me a friend request  https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=100051472509515
I wish I could give you my Instagram, but believe it or not, I don't know how to use it.
